volumes.localDesc:
Belobog History and Culture Museum
Volunteer Guide Application Form

NAME
Gepard Landau

PAST EXPERIENCE
In 6█5 AF, graduated from School of Social Science in the Belobog Cadet School, and obtained a bachelor's degree in Modern Military Science. In the same year, began serving the Silvermane Guards.
In 6█7 AF, obtained major merit in the military campaign in the north. Began serving as the Silvermane Guard Captain in the same year until now.

SPECIAL SKILLS
Cultivating flowers
